From wolfg@ng@viechtb@uer @ending from m@@@trichtuniver@ity@nl  Tue Jul 10 11:25:39 2018
From: wolfg@ng@viechtb@uer @ending from m@@@trichtuniver@ity@nl (Viechtbauer, Wolfgang (SP))
